" Reorder a comma separated (CSV) file:
:%s/\([^,]*\),\([^,]*\),\([^,]*\),\(.*\)/\1,\3 \4,\2/
" Or slightly clearer:
:%s:\([^,]*\),\([^,]*\),\([^,]*\),\(.*\):\1,\3 \4,\2:
" Then remove the spaces:
s/[ \t]*,[ \t]*/,/g

" Change really, really, really or really, really, really, really... to very
:%s/\(really \)\(really \)*/very /

