RGB hex  FF=100%  CC=80%  99=60%  66=40%  33=20%  00=0%
E.g. #00FF00 is 0% red, 100% green, 0% blue
or RGB:
00 is no color (black #000000), FF is full color (white #FFFFFF)

Byte size increments: mega, giga, tera, peta, exa, zetta, yotta

